long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A simple discord app to help out people leave servers easily in bulk, due to limitations of available discord API, we have to pick the token from the request headers.

This has been something that a widespread of people demand.

We are NOT AT ALL saving the token of the user
